creator: Do It Myself
descriptionHtml:
The Phone is a call management application that helps you quickly make calls as you want, receive calls instantly, with an intuitive interface.

Main function:
- Manage favorite calls: make calls to your loved ones quickly, easily add favorite calls
- Manage recent calls, missed calls
- Manage contacts
- Create a new call
- Blocked Contacts allows you to identify unwanted callers and blocks phone

We always make the app better every day. Please share with your friends to support us. Thank you!
